CustomField.description: The latitude component of the entity's location defined as the angular distance of the primary physical address north or south from the Earth's equator expressed in decimal numbers. Positive numbers indicate degrees north. Negative numbers indicate degrees south.

CustomField.label: Primary Address Latitude
